research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Crawford town, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro Tem, and four Council Members. Information was gathered from the City of Crawford's official website and verified with the Texas Municipal League and Texas State Directory. The May 3, 2025, general election for Mayor and two Councilmembers was canceled due to unopposed candidates, confirming the continued terms of Bobby Bain as Mayor, and Lewis Snow and John Weldon as Councilmembers.
